### Event Service demo (via API Gateway)
###
### 1) Get an access token (see scripts/test-api.sh), then paste it below:
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. POST create event (requires staff role)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Mindfulness Workshop",
  "description": "A guided mindfulness session for students.",
  "date": "2025-11-15T10:00:00",
  "location": "Toronto",
  "capacity": 30,
  "resourceIds": [1, 2]
}

### 2. GET event by ID (replace {id})
GET http://localhost:8082/api/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Search by location
GET http://localhost:8082/api/events/search/location?loc=Toronto
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
